These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Sport: skiing, badminton, parkour, biathlon
Transport: jet-ski, train, van, trike
1. Transport:trike is on the left of Sport:parkour##1
2. Sport:skiing is on the left of Transport:train##1
3. Sport:biathlon is in an odd position##4
4. Transport:van is on the left or right of Transport:trike##3
5. Sport:skiing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | skiing | badminton | biathlon | parkour |
| Transport        | jet-ski | train   | trike | van    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Sport: ice-hockey, surfing, climbing, skiing
Beverage: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, fanta
1. Sport:surfing is on the left of Sport:skiing##1
2. Beverage:almond-milk is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
3. Beverage:lemonade is in an odd position##4
4. Beverage:almond-milk == Sport:ice-hockey##1
5. Beverage:coffee is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1
6. Beverage:almond-milk == Sport:ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Sport   | climbing | ice-hockey  | surfing  | skiing |
| Beverage   | fanta    | almond-milk | lemonade | coffee    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
House: ranch-style, tower, wooden, craftsman
Color: brown, black, blue, orange
1. House:craftsman is on the left or right of Color:orange##3
2. House:wooden is in an even position##4
3. Color:orange is on the left or right of House:tower##3
4. Color:orange is on the right of Color:blue##1
5. Color:brown is in an odd position##4
6. House:tower is on the right of House:wooden##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| House          | craftsman | wooden | tower    | ranch-style      |
| Color   | blue        | orange     | brown | black |

