4. Flower:daisy is on the right of City:prague##1
5. Flower:amaryllis is between Flower:daisy and Flower:marigold##2
6. City:hamburg is in an odd position##4
7. City:hamburg is between Flower:amaryllis and City:marseilles##2
8. Flower:amaryllis is on the left or right of Flower:marigold##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
